attributes.description: This dashboard shows event logs collected by the Check Point Harmony Email & Collaboration integration.

params.markdown:
**Navigation**

**Check Point Harmony Email & Collaboration**

**Overview**

This dashboard provides an overview of key metrics and insights derived from event logs generated by the Check Point Harmony Email & Collaboration integration, displaying key statistics such as top customers and sender addresses, event trends over time, and a breakdown of events by type, saas, state, and confidence indicator, as well as essential details about the event data.

[**Integration Page**](/app/integrations/detail/checkpoint_email/overview)
